    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Demon clan, Level 8+, Having never used the <strong>Bloody Feast</strong> clan feature</p><ul><li>The sun no longer damages you, but you lose the bloody feast feature, replacing it with a new feature <strong>Demons slumber.</strong></li><li>you no longer have your regeration dice go down a step from the <strong>Demonic Stomach</strong> clan feature.</li><li><strong>Demons slumber:</strong> twice per long rest, you may as a full turn action, regain 3 hit dice as you lie down for a nap.</li></ul>",
